Package net.sourceforge.aglets.itinerary.helpers

Class Summary
BaseCircularItinerary An itinerary that loops over destinations, thus the agent always has a next destination.
BaseCircularTaskItinerary This class represents a task itinerary that loops over destination, thus the agent has always a next destination.
BaseItinerary This class represents the base class for more complex itinerary.
BaseRandomItinerary This class represents a random itinerary, that is an itinerary which chose randomly the next destination.
BaseTask This class represents a base implementation for the Task interface, it's a kind of Task adapter.
BaseTaskItinerary This class represents the base for the construction of a task-based itinerary, that is an itinerary with task associated.
